description:
Is peace on Earth a possibility? In this fast-paced, stress-filled life, its near impossible to imagine peace at all. Yet, Scripture tells us we can have peace today, through Jesus Christ. #Shorts #YouTubeShorts 

Listen as Pastor Ted Wilson shares insights about the fifth, sixth, and seventh blessings from Thoughts from the Mount of Blessing by Adventist pioneer Ellen White: https://youtu.be/8aJijYxbjbI.
